# Frontend

- Vite + React + TypeScript in `frontend/`
- Two layouts: `PublicLayout` (seeker: `/`, `/search`, `/jobs/:id`) and `OpsLayout` (`/ops/*`)
- Pages: `frontend/src/pages/public/` and `frontend/src/pages/ops/`
- API client in `frontend/src/api/` - types mirror backend DTOs; `useSearch` → `GET /api/search`
- TanStack Query for data fetching; poll scrape overview 5s when active, 30s otherwise
- Dev proxy: `/api` → `http://localhost:50423` in `frontend/vite.config.ts`
- Shared components in `frontend/src/components/`
- Do not add write endpoints or auth in v1 - UI is read-only against existing API (except ops enrichment backfill is API-only)
- After changes: `npm run build` is sufficient. Do not start `npm run dev` unless the user asks.
